{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat/resolvedOptions","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">Standard-Objekte</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl\"><code>Intl</code></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/@@toStringTag\"><code>Intl[@@toStringTag]</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/getCanonicalLocales\"><code>Intl.getCanonicalLocales()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/supportedValuesOf\"><code>Intl.supportedValuesOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li><li><strong>Ähnliche Seiten:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Collator\"><code>Intl.Collator</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/ListFormat\"><code>Intl.ListFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/NumberFormat\"><code>Intl.NumberFormat</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/PluralRules\"><code>Intl.PluralRules</code></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/RelativeTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.RelativeTimeFormat</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/Segmenter\"><code>Intl.Segmenter</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong>Vererbung:</strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a></strong></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Eigenschaften</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/constructor\"><code>Object.prototype.constructor</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/proto\"><code>Object.prototype.__proto__</code></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Methoden</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()</code></strong> Methode gibt ein Objekt mit den Eigenschaften zum Gebiet und der Datums- und Zeitformatierung zurück, die beim der Initialisierung eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>DateTimeFormat</code></a> Objektes berechnet werden.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/intl-datetimeformat-prototype-resolvedoptions.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>dateTimeFormat</var>.resolvedOptions()</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein neues Objekt mit den Eigenschaften zum Gebiet und der Datums- und Zeitformatierung, die beim der Initialisierung eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>DateTimeFormat</code></a> Objektes berechnet werden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das resultierende Objekt hat die folgenden Eigenschaften:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"locale\"><code>locale</code></dt>\n <dd>Der BCP 47 Sprach-Tag für die genutzte Sprache. Wenn Unicode-Erweiterungen im BCP 47 Sprach-Tag enthalten waren, die für die Sprache unterstützt werden, sind die Unterstützen Schlüssel-Werte-Paare in <code>locale</code> enthalten.</dd>\n <dt id=\"calendar\"><code>calendar</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"numberingsystem\"><code>numberingSystem</code></dt>\n <dd>Dieser Wert wird durch die Unicode-Erweiterungsschlüssel <code>\"ca\"</code> und <code>\"nu\"</code> oder mit einem Standardwert gefüllt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"timezone\"><code>timeZone</code></dt>\n <dd>Die Wert für die Unterstützen Eigenschaft im <code>options</code> Argument; <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> (entspricht der Standard-Zeitzone der Laufzeitumgebung), wenn keine verwendet wird. Warnung: Anwendungen sollten nicht auf den Rückgabewert <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/undefined\"><code>undefined</code></a> programmiert sein, weil es in zukünftigen Versionen sein kann, dass ein <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> zurückgegeben wird, der die Standard-Zeitzone der Laufzeitumgebung identifiziert.</dd>\n <dt id=\"hour12\"><code>hour12</code></dt>\n <dd>Der Wert der verwendeten Eigenschaft im <code>options</code> Argument oder ein Standard-Wert.</dd>\n <dt id=\"weekday\"><code>weekday</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"era\"><code>era</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"year\"><code>year</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"month\"><code>month</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"day\"><code>day</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"hour\"><code>hour</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"minute\"><code>minute</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"second\"><code>second</code></dt>\n <dt id=\"timezonename\"><code>timeZoneName</code></dt>\n <dd>Die Werte resultieren von den Eigenschaften in dem <code>options</code> Argument und den möglichen Kombinationen und Repräsentationen der Datums- und Zeitformatierung aus der ausgewählte Sprache. Einige der Eigenschaften können auch fehlen, was bedeutet, dass die Komponenten nicht in der formatierten Ausgabe enthalten sind.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"einsatz_der_resolvedoptions_methode","title":"Einsatz der <code>resolvedOptions</code> Methode","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> germanFakeRegion <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Intl<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>DateTimeFormat</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'de-XX'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">timeZone</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'UTC'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> usedOptions <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> germanFakeRegion<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">resolvedOptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nusedOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>locale<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>          <span class=\"token comment\">// \"de\"</span>\nusedOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>calendar<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// \"gregory\"</span>\nusedOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>numberingSystem<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"latn\"</span>\nusedOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>timeZone<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>        <span class=\"token comment\">// \"UTC\"</span>\nusedOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>month<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>           <span class=\"token comment\">// \"numeric\"</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Einsatz der resolvedOptions Methode"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/1.0/#sec-12.3.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 1.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-402/2.0/#sec-Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API 2.0 (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma402/#sec-Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript Internationalization API (ECMA-402)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Intl.DateTimeFormat.resolvedOptions","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat/resolvedOptions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl/DateTimeFormat\"><code>Intl.DateTimeFormat</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions() Methode gibt ein Objekt mit den Eigenschaften zum Gebiet und der Datums- und Zeitformatierung zurück, die beim der Initialisierung eines DateTimeFormat Objektes berechnet werden.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Intl.DateTimeFormat.prototype.resolvedOptions()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/datetimeformat/resolvedoptions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/intl/datetimeformat/resolvedoptions/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript-Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Globale Objekte"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Intl","title":"Intl"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Refe